{% extends 'public/layout.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}
<!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
<header id="hero" class="hero-ipg">
    <div class="hero-ipg__bg" style="background-image: url('/images/image12.jpg');"></div>
    <div class="container-lg hero-ipg__content">
        <h1 class="hero-ipg__title">Therapies</h1>
        <p class="hero-ipg__sub">Explore therapeutic approaches that prioritize well-being, awareness, and transformation.</p>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- ================= SEÇÃO PSICANÁLISE ================= -->
<section id="psicanalise" class="py-5">
    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/Psicanalise.jpeg" alt="Psicanálise" class="img-fluid rounded shadow"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Psychoanalyst: a deep and reflective approach to emotional wellbeing</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Psychoanalysis is a well-established and reflective approach focused on gaining a deeper understanding of the human mind, emotions, and patterns of behaviour. Its purpose is to expand individual awareness of the internal processes that influence choices, relationships, and the way each person engages with life.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    This approach is grounded in qualified listening and a continuous reflective process, aimed at understanding internal narratives, significant experiences, and unconscious content that shape thoughts, emotional responses, and behaviours over time. This journey supports the recognition of patterns, the understanding of internal conflicts, and the development of a more conscious relationship with oneself.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Sessions take place in a confidential, ethical, and respectful setting, based on dialogue and reflection. Clients are invited to express themselves freely and consciously, fostering a gradual deepening of self-awareness and emotional clarity.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Psychoanalysis is suited for individuals who value depth, reflection, and continuous personal development. The process supports meaningful transformation, enhancing wellbeing, emotional autonomy, and the quality of personal and professional relationships.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Highlight:
                    Psychoanalysis expands awareness of the internal processes that influence choices, relationships, and the way we engage with the world.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= SEÇÃO TERAPIA INTEGRATIVA ================= -->
<section id="terapia-integrativa" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="row align-items-center flex-md-row-reverse">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/Terapia-integrativa.jpeg" alt="Terapia Integrativa"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Integrative Therapy: a personalised and multidimensional approach to wellbeing</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Integrative Therapy is a comprehensive and personalised approach that considers the individual across multiple dimensions, such as emotions, cognitive patterns, behaviours, and life context. Its purpose is to offer a process adapted to the uniqueness of each client, respecting their needs, experiences, and objectives.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    This approach integrates different methodologies in a coherent and strategic way, fostering greater internal clarity, emotional balance, and alignment between thoughts, emotions, and choices. The process is guided by attentive listening, reflective dialogue, and personal development tools, always in a conscious and personalised manner.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    The process is conducted on an individual basis, respecting each client’s uniqueness, life moment, and objectives, supporting a consistent integration between personal values and practical actions in everyday life.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Integrative Therapy is suited for individuals seeking a refined, personalised, and in-depth experience, focused on wellbeing, internal integration, and a more intentional, balanced, and sustainable way of living.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Highlight:
                    A personalised approach that integrates multiple dimensions of the individual to promote clarity, balance, and wellbeing.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= SEÇÃO COACHING ================= -->
<section id="coaching" class="py-5">
    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/Coaching.jpeg" alt="Coaching" class="img-fluid rounded shadow"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Personal Development Coaching: clarity, awareness, and personal growth</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Personal Development Coaching is a structured approach focused on personal growth, designed for individuals who wish to expand self-awareness, strengthen autonomy, and promote consistent and conscious change in their lives.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    This process integrates reflection, self-knowledge, and practical direction, supporting clients in identifying values, priorities, personal goals, and internal patterns that influence choices, behaviours, and everyday experiences.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Sessions are conducted in a personalised manner, respecting each client’s moment, rhythm, and individual needs. The focus is on building internal clarity, emotional balance, and alignment between intentions, decisions, and actions.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Personal Development Coaching contributes to wellbeing by fostering personal responsibility, self-confidence, and internal organisation. It is suited for individuals seeking conscious growth, greater presence, and a life that is coherent with their values, purpose, and way of living.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Highlight:
                    Personal Development Coaching supports more conscious choices and a life aligned with one’s values and priorities.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}

{% block inline_javascripts %}
<script>
    AOS.init();

    (() => {
        const nav = document.getElementById('mainNavbar');
        const hero = document.getElementById('hero');
        const bg = document.querySelector('.hero-ipg__bg');
        const content = document.querySelector('.hero-ipg__content');

        function onScroll(){
            const y = window.scrollY || 0;

            nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', y > 10);

            if (hero && bg){
                const heroH = hero.offsetHeight;
                const p = Math.min(1, y / heroH);
                bg.style.transform = `translateY(${y * 0.25}px) scale(1.06)`;

                if (content){
                    content.style.opacity = (1 - p * 0.55).toFixed(3);
                    content.style.transform = `translateY(${p * 18}px)`;
                }
            }
        }

        window.addEventListener('scroll', onScroll, { passive:true });
        onScroll();
    })();
</script>
{% endblock %}
